(this is for shadowbane) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#460000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ushinkaiobr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shin Kai OBR</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#9C0000>(3/29/01 9:07:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fsbobrfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=56.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Peers into the shadows.</span><hr size=1> Shin-Kai stands with his back to the corner of a stone house. Down the street of poorly lit cobblestones stands Valdrin. Hearing Valdrins plee to the shadows of the night, Shin-Kai slowly sleaths Nai-Toge, his blade. There is only the hiss of its perfect edge as it slides into the dark folds of Shin-Kai's cloak. Valdrin turns as his ears pick up the sound. He wonders over towards the corner, slowly. Shin-Kai covers his face with the lower half of his mask covering his mouth and nose. Valdrin approaches. Valdrin pulls from his belt a dirk of fine steel. Shin-Kai leaps silently on top of a barrel and then to the beam that runs the middle of the roof. The beam extends out over the street and Shin-Kai waits. His body arched like a cat ready for the pounce. Valdrin jumps out around the corner with his blade ready, but there is no one there to greet him save the east wind. While leaning over Shin-Kai tosses a single throwing dagger into the air. It rises, dancing in the air. Pausing at its peek it gleams in the moon light and falls. Shin-kai watched it as it danced, but only for a moment. Wasting no time he sped across the thatched roof and into the shadows unoticed. Just as Valdrin put away his dirk the dagger from above stuck perfectly into the barrel before him. On its hilt carved beautifully is a single black rose. It was no answer but aleast Valdrin knows he was heard and that is enough. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ushinkaiobr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shin Kai OBR</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10> at: 3/29/01 7:09:52 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bsbobr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=valdrin>Valdrin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#9C0000>(3/29/01 9:47:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fsbobrfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=56.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Peers into the shadows.</span><hr size=1> After the encounter with the unknown member of the black rose Valdrin understands his foolishness in thinking this would be easy. He picks up the dagger admiring the workmanship on it. 'Well it seems this is the place I have been looking for to fine tune my skills.'I suppose they will know where to find me' he says to himself as he heads back to the tavern. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#460000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bsbobr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=valdrin>Valdrin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#9C0000>(3/30/01 11:15:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fsbobrfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=56.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   The next morning</span><hr size=1> Valdrin wakes up the next morning with thoughts of how he would gain the trust and friendship of OBR. Knowing that to do such a thing would require meeting them. Valdrin leaves the desk hearing a knock at the door.&quot;yes can I help you&quot; Valdrin says to a young lady.<br>
&quot;I apologize for the interupption mi'lord. We have been having trouble with thieves and Was asked to make sure you are ok. A grim smile crosses Valdrin's face as he says &quot;Mi'lady I assure you nothing is missing.&quot; HE quickly shuts the door on her and returns to the desk. &quot;Damn it!&quot; realizing that the note he had just wrote is now gone. &quot;hmm it appears not even I can keep my stuff&quot; he laughs. <br>
As the figure heads back to his leader he reads the note.<br>
<br>
Members of the order of the black rose. I have come in search for that rare thing amoung us called honor. I like many of you kill for a living. I offer you my loyalty and knowledge. You ask what I want in return? Just one thing A chance to prove myself to you. A chance to join you in the shadows. If you wish to contact me I can be reached at 104077290 room ICQ. I await a answer .<br>
<br>
Valdrin of Garlon<br>
