<br>
Looking at the note, Valdrin notices an emblem of a black rose on the letter. Opening the note, he reads&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Valdrin,<br>
<br>
You seek a organization that prides itself of secrecy and profit. When most people fear the shadows, we embrace it. Do you, Valdrin, embrace the shadows?  Can you feel her comforting darkness surround you?<br>
<br>
Only a few can truly understand the gifts that the Shadow brings us. If you truly want to be a part of us, then you must be prepared to take the shadow upon thine breast.  Also, you must be prepared to fully follow some missions that may or may not be your nature.  But rest assured, everything is done in honor of the Shadow and the Dollar.<br>
<br>
