<br>
Anyone can be a petty thief, or a murderer, but it takes talent to make a successful Rogue.  The Order can help you achieve your goals, as well as provide a unique climate to thrive.<br>
<br>
There must be honor amongst Thieves, everyone else is fair game.&quot;<br>
<br>
